# 🌿 Letter to Future Me

A calming, interactive micro-site where you can send a note to your future self — wrapped in magic, movement, and earthy visuals.

![preview](./preview.png) <!-- You can upload a preview image and update the path -->

---

## ✨ Features

- 🌱 **Minimalist Contact Form** – Only one field: your email, to write your future self.
- 🌸 **Plant Emoji Animations** – Leaves and plants sprout when you interact with elements.
- 🪄 **Magic Cursor Trail** – Cursor sparkles with soft glowing particles.
- 🌼 **Flower Typing Animation** – Words blossom as you type.
- 🌍 **Earthy Themed UI** – Soothing colors and animated floral backgrounds.
- ✅ **Form Validation** – Ensures you don’t forget your email.

